				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "A repeated sequential AD for the manip Nestor, where he talks to himself after it was revealed that there were explosives inside donated toys. He stays near the chest (or in the place where it was, if the player blew it up). \r\nNote: toys may be taken from the crate or the crate itself could be exploded, so we should not refer to them rather than vaguely."
				}
